#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; is a geographical atlas and a virtual globe which lets you quickly "
"explore places on our home planet. You can use &marble; to look up "
"addresses, to easily create maps, measure distances and to retrieve detail "
"information about locations that you have just heard about in the news or on "
"the Internet. The user interface is clean, simple and easy to use."
msgstr ""
"&marble; je geografski atlas in virtualni globus, ki vam omogoča hitro "
"raziskovanje krajev na našem planetu. Uporabite lahko &marble; za iskanje "
"naslovov, enostavno ustvarjanje zemljevidov, merjenje razdalj in "
"pridobivanje podrobnih informacij o lokacijah, za katere ste pravkar slišali "
"v novicah ali na internetu. Uporabniški vmesnik je čist, preprost in "
"enostaven za uporabo."

