#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Welcome to &marble;, a small interactive globe and geographical atlas that "
"puts the world at your fingertips. Just like a real atlas or a conventional "
"globe &marble; allows you to freely move across its map and lookup places. "
"Furthermore &marble; allows you to zoom in and have many different views on "
"the surface for the <guilabel>Earth</guilabel> or the <guilabel>Moon</"
"guilabel> (with his view). In its default configuration &marble; offers 15 "
"different views: <guilabel>Atlas</guilabel>, <guilabel>OpenStreetMap</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Satellite View</guilabel>, <guilabel>Earth at Night</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Behaim Globe 1492</guilabel>, <guilabel>Sentinel2 "
"Satellite Map</guilabel>, <guilabel>Historical Map 1689</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Political Map</guilabel>, <guilabel>Plain Map</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Precipitation (December)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Precipitation "
"(July)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Temperature (December)</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Temperature (July)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Vector OSM</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Moon</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Dobrodošli v &marble;, majhnem interaktivnem globusu in geografskem atlasu, "
"s katerim imate svet na dosegu roke. Tako kot pravi atlas ali običajni "
"globus &marble; omogoča prosto premikanje po zemljevidu in mestih iskanja. "
"Poleg tega vam &marble; omogoča povečavo in veliko različnih pogledov na "
"površje <guilabel>Zemlje</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Lune</guilabel> (z njenim "
"pogledom). V privzeti konfiguraciji &marble; ponuja 15 različnih pogledov: "
"<guilabel>Atlas</guilabel>, <guilabel>OpenStreetMap</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Satelitski pogled</guilabel>, <guilabel>Zemlja ponoči</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Behaim Globe 1492 </guilabel>, <guilabel>Satelitski zemljevid "
"Sentinel2</guilabel>, <guilabel>Zgodovinski zemljevid 1689</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Politični zemljevid</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navadni zemljevid</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel> Padavine (december)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Padavine "
"(julij)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Temperatura (december)</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Temperatura (julij)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Vektorski OSM </"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Luna</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; comes with a small database of more than 12,000 locations (cities, "
"mountains, volcanoes) which can be searched for and which are integrated "
"with Wikipedia. Additionally you can measure distances using &marble; "
"between multiple measure points which can be set freely."
msgstr ""
"&marble; prihaja z majhno zbirko podatkov z več kot 12.000 lokacijami "
"(mesta, gore, vulkani), ki jih je mogoče iskati in so integrirane z "
"Wikipedijo. Poleg tega lahko merite razdalje z &marble; med več merilnimi "
"točkami, ki jih je mogoče prosto nastaviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; is free software and licensed under the &GNU; Lesser General Public "
"License."
msgstr ""
"&marble; je prosta programska oprema in licencirana pod &GNU; Manjša splošna "
"javna licenca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; quick start guide: Navigation"
msgstr "&marble; vodnik za hiter začetek: Navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is &marble; the first time you run it, either with "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Applications</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Education</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>&kde; &marble; (Virtual Globe)</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> from the global menu or with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> and entering <command>marble</command> into "
"the input field."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je &marble; ko ga prvič zaženete, bodisi z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Aplikacije</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Izobraževanje</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>&kde; &marble; (Navidezni globus)</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> iz globalnega menija ali s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> in vnosom <command>marble</command> v vnosno "
"polje."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&marble; main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&marble; glavno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&marble; main window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&marble; glavno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right you can see a topographical map of our beautiful home planet. "
"To allow for better orientation the map offers a scale bar in the lower left "
"corner as well as a windrose on the top right. To navigate and to control "
"the view you can use the tools on the <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel> info "
"box at the right: Press the arrow buttons to rotate the globe. The "
"<guibutton>Up</guibutton> and <guibutton>Down</guibutton> arrow buttons will "
"tilt the earth axis back and forth. The <guibutton>Left</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Right</guibutton> arrow buttons will make the earth spin around "
"its physical axis."
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani lahko vidite topografski zemljevid našega čudovitega "
"domačega planeta. Za boljšo orientacijo zemljevid ponuja merilno vrstico v "
"spodnjem levem kotu in rožo vetrov v zgornjem desnem kotu. Za navigacijo in "
"nadzor pogleda lahko uporabite orodja v oknu z informacijami "
"<guilabel>Navigacija</guilabel> na desni: Pritisnite gumbe s puščicami, da "
"zavrtite globus. Gumba s puščicama <guibutton>Gor</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Dol</guibutton> bosta nagnila zemeljsko os naprej in nazaj. Z "
"gumboma <guibutton>levo</guibutton> in <guibutton>desno</guibutton> se bo "
"zemlja zavrtela okoli svoje fizične osi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can accomplish the same behavior by pressing the &LMB; somewhere on the "
"globe and by moving the mouse while keeping the &LMB; pressed. Using this "
"drag and drop style navigation will allow you to adjust the viewing angle "
"much easier and more precisely. The cursor keys on your keyboard offer "
"another alternative way to quickly change directions."
msgstr ""
"Enako vedenje lahko dosežete s pritiskom na &LMB; nekje na zemeljski obli in "
"s premikanjem miške, medtem ko držite &LMB; stisnjen. Uporaba te navigacije "
"v slogu povleci in spusti vam bo omogočila veliko lažjo in natančnejšo "
"nastavitev kota gledanja. Kazalne tipke na tipkovnici ponujajo še en "
"alternativni način za hitro spreminjanje smeri."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Zoom in and out by moving the vertical slider up and down. If your mouse has "
"got a mouse wheel you can use that one instead - or you just hold the &LMB; "
"and the &RMB; down both at once while moving the mouse up and down. Changing "
"the zoom level step by step can be done via the <guibutton>Zoom In</"
"guibutton> and <guibutton>Zoom Out</guibutton> buttons which are placed "
"above and below the zoom slider (or using the <keycap>+</keycap> and "
"<keycap>-</keycap> keys on your keyboard)."
msgstr ""
"Povečajte in pomanjšajte zemljevid s premikanjem navpičnega drsnika navzgor "
"in navzdol. Če ima vaša miška kolesce miške, lahko namesto njega uporabite "
"to - ali pa samo držite &LMB; in &RMB; oboje hkrati, medtem ko premikate "
"miško gor in dol. Spreminjanje stopnje povečave korak za korakom lahko "
"izvedete z gumboma <guibutton>Povečaj</guibutton> in <guibutton>Pomanjšaj</"
"guibutton>, ki sta nameščena nad in pod drsnikom za povečavo (ali z uporabo "
"<keycap>+</keycap> in <keycap>-</keycap> tipki na tipkovnici)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the map's resolution zooming in will provide you with more "
"detail. Smaller cities will appear and using the topographic map you might "
"notice that coastlines are provided as vector graphics."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od ločljivosti zemljevida vam bo povečava zagotovila več "
"podrobnosti. Prikazala se bodo manjša mesta in na topografskem zemljevidu "
"boste morda opazili, da so obale prikazane kot vektorska grafika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you should get lost you can always reset the viewing angle and zoom "
"level back to the point where we started off: Just press the "
"<guibutton>Home</guibutton> button (or the &Home; button on your keyboard). "
"To set the home location to the current position (center of the map) select "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Home Location</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če bi se izgubili, lahko vedno ponastavite vidni kot in stopnjo povečave "
"nazaj na točko, kjer smo začeli: Samo pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Home</"
"guibutton> (ali gumb &Home; na tipkovnici). Če želite nastaviti domačo "
"lokacijo na trenutni položaj (sredina zemljevida), izberite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavi domačo "
"lokacijo</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A click onto the status bar using the &RMB; offers a menu which lets you "
"customize the appearance of the status bar. You can show the position, "
"altitude, the current tile level and a progress indicator that displays the "
"status of the map data download."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na statusno vrstico z &RMB; ponuja meni, ki vam omogoča "
"prilagajanje videza statusne vrstice. Prikažete lahko položaj, nadmorsko "
"višino, trenutno raven ploščic in indikator napredka, ki prikazuje stanje "
"prenosa podatkov zemljevida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing different map views for &marble;"
msgstr "Izbira različnih pogledov zemljevida za &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; comes with 15 different views: <guilabel>Atlas</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>OpenStreetMap</guilabel>, <guilabel>Satellite View</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Earth at Night</guilabel>, <guilabel>Behaim Globe 1492</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Sentinel2 Satellite Map</guilabel>, <guilabel>Historical Map 1689</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Political Map</guilabel>, <guilabel>Plain Map</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Precipitation (December)</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Precipitation (July)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Temperature (December)</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Temperature (July)</guilabel> <guilabel>Vector OSM</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Moon</guilabel>. You can choose among these by "
"pressing the <guilabel>Map View</guilabel> tab on the top of &marble;'s "
"toolbox:"
msgstr ""
"&marble; ima 15 različnih pogledov: <guilabel>Atlas</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>OpenStreetMap</guilabel>, <guilabel>Satelitski pogled</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Zemlja ponoči</guilabel>, <guilabel>Behaim Globe 1492</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Satelitski zemljevid Sentinel2</guilabel>, <guilabel>Zgodovinski "
"zemljevid 1689</guilabel>, <guilabel>Politični zemljevid</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Navadni zemljevid</guilabel>, <guilabel >Padavine (december)</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Padavine (julij)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Temperatura "
"(december)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Temperatura (julij)</guilabel> "
"<guilabel>Vektorski OSM </guilabel> in <guilabel>Luna</guilabel>. Med temi "
"lahko izbirate tako, da pritisnete zavihek <guilabel>Pogled zemljevida</"
"guilabel> na vrhu orodne vrstice &marble;:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; map views"
msgstr "&marble; pogledi zemljevidov"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Map Views"
msgstr "&marble; Pogledi zemljevidov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Atlas</guilabel>: A classic topographic map. It uses vector lines "
"( \"MicroWorldDataBase II\" ) to mark coastlines, country borders &etc; and "
"bitmap graphics ( \"SRTM30\" ) to create the height relief."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Atlas</guilabel>: klasična topografska karta. Uporablja vektorske "
"črte (\"MicroWorldDataBase II\") za označevanje obal, državnih meja itd. in "
"bitne grafike (\"SRTM30\") za ustvarjanje višinskega reliefa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>OpenStreetMap</guilabel>: A global roadmap created by the "
"OpenStreetMap (OSM) project. OSM is an open community which creates free "
"editable maps. The OSM data was rendered using Mapnik."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>OpenStreetMap</guilabel>: Globalni zemljevid, ustvarjen s "
"projektom OpenStreetMap (OSM). OSM je odprta skupnost, ki ustvarja proste "
"zemljevide, ki jih je mogoče urejati. Podatki OSM so bili upodobljeni z "
"uporabo Mapnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Satellite View</guilabel>: Earth as seen from Space. The map is "
"based on NASA's beautiful <ulink url=\"https://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/"
"features/BlueMarble/\">Blue &marble; Next Generation</ulink> pictures. "
"Credits: NASA’s Earth Observatory"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Satelitski pogled</guilabel>: Zemlja kot je vidna iz vesolja. "
"Zemljevid temelji na Nasinem čudovitem <ulink url=\"https://earthobservatory."
"nasa.gov/features/BlueMarble/\">Blue &marble; Slike naslednje generacije</"
"ulink>. Zasluge: Nasin observatorij Zemlje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Earth at Night</guilabel>: This image of Earth’s city lights was "
"created with data from the Defense Meteorological Satellite Program (DMSP) "
"Operational Linescan System (OLS)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zemlja ponoči</guilabel>: ta slika mestnih luči Zemlje je bila "
"ustvarjena s podatki iz operativnega sistema za pregledovanje linij (OLS) "
"obrambnega meteorološkega satelitskega programa (DMSP)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Behaim Globe 1492</guilabel>: Produced by Martin Behaim from 1490–"
"1492, it is the oldest surviving terrestrial globe."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Behaimov globus 1492</guilabel>: Izdelal ga je Martin Behaim med "
"leti 1490–1492 in je najstarejši ohranjeni zemeljski globus."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Sentinel2 Satellite Map</guilabel>: Based on the Sentinel data, "
"see more information <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Marble/"
"Sentinel2MapTheme\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Satelitski zemljevid Sentinel2</guilabel>: Na podlagi podatkov "
"Sentinel si oglejte več informacij <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Marble/Sentinel2MapTheme\">tukaj</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Historical Map 1689</guilabel>: A historical world map from the "
"year 1689 created by G. van Schagen in Amsterdam."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zgodovinski zemljevid 1689</guilabel>: Zgodovinski zemljevid sveta "
"iz leta 1689, ki ga je ustvaril G. van Schagen v Amsterdamu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Political Map</guilabel>: A simple map with the current frontiers "
"of countries."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Politični zemljevid</guilabel>: preprost zemljevid s trenutnimi "
"mejami držav."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Plain Map</guilabel>: A plain map. It uses vector lines to mark "
"coastlines and country borders &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Navaden zemljevid</guilabel>: Navaden zemljevid. Uporablja "
"vektorske črte za označevanje obal in državnih meja itd."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Precipitation (December)</guilabel>: A map which shows the average "
"precipitation in December."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Padavine (december)</guilabel>: Zemljevid, ki prikazuje povprečno "
"količino padavin v decembru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Precipitation (July)</guilabel>: A map which shows the average "
"precipitation (rain, snow, hail, &etc;) in July."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Padavine (julij)</guilabel>: Zemljevid, ki prikazuje povprečno "
"količino padavin (dež, sneg, toča, &etc;) v juliju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Temperature (December)</guilabel>: A map which shows the average "
"temperature in December."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Temperatura (december)</guilabel>: Zemljevid, ki prikazuje "
"povprečno temperaturo v decembru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Temperature (July)</guilabel>: A map which shows the average "
"temperature in July."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Temperatura (julij)</guilabel>: Zemljevid, ki prikazuje povprečno "
"temperaturo v juliju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Vector OSM</guilabel>: Vector map from the <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.openstreetmap.org/\">OpenStreetMap project</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vektorski OSM</guilabel>: Vektorski zemljevid iz <ulink url="
"\"https:/www.openstreetmap.org/\">projekta OpenStreetMap</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Moon</guilabel>: A map of the moon. The map is based on data from "
"the Clementine Moon mission (UVVIS Basemap Mosaic). Credits: NASA/SDIO, "
"Courtesy USGS Astrogeology Research Program."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Luna</guilabel>: zemljevid lune. Zemljevid temelji na podatkih "
"misije Clementine Moon (UVVIS Basemap Mosaic). Zasluge: NASA/SDIO, z "
"dovoljenjem USGS Astrogeology Research Program."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching places using &marble;"
msgstr "Iskanje krajev z &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; comes with a small database of more than 12,000 cities (from <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.populationdata.net/monde/\"></ulink>) and a few mountains "
"and volcanoes. You can find a location by entering its name into the search "
"line on the top of the toolbox (&marble; always uses the native name in "
"Latin letters). As you start typing, suggestions below the search line will "
"appear like this:"
msgstr ""
"&marble; prihaja z majhno bazo podatkov z več kot 12.000 mesti (iz <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.populationdata.net/monde/\"></ulink>) ter nekaj gorami in "
"vulkani. Lokacijo lahko poiščete tako, da vnesete njeno ime v iskalno "
"vrstico na vrhu orodjarne (&marble; vedno uporablja domače ime v latinici). "
"Ko začnete tipkati, se bodo predlogi pod iskalno vrstico prikazali takole:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; searching places"
msgstr "&marble; iskanje krajev"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Searching Places"
msgstr "&marble; Iskanje krajev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you hit &Enter;, &marble; runners will also query both online and offline "
"searches to return you even more useful data."
msgstr ""
"Ko pritisnete &Enter;, bodo tekači &marble; prav tako iskali v spletu in "
"zunaj njega, da vam vrnejo še več uporabnih podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following online search runners are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednji spletni iskalniki:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Nominatim: An online search and reverse geocoding service, using data from "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org\"></ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Nominatim: storitev spletnega iskanja in povratnega geokodiranja, ki "
"uporablja podatke iz <ulink url=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org\"></ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"HostIP: A reverse geocoding based on IP address, using data from <ulink url="
"\"https://www.hostip.info\"></ulink>"
msgstr ""
"HostIP: obratno geokodiranje na podlagi naslova IP z uporabo podatkov iz "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.hostip.info\"></ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following offline search runners are also available, depending on extra "
"software and data you have installed:"
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so tudi naslednji izvajalci iskanja brez povezave, odvisno od "
"dodatne programske opreme in podatkov, ki ste jih namestili:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Local Database: All placemarks in all open documents will be searched for. "
"This includes your Bookmarks of course."
msgstr ""
"Lokalna zbirka podatkov: Iskane bodo vse oznake položaja v vseh odprtih "
"dokumentih. To seveda vključuje vaše zaznamke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Monav: An offline search service using the data from Monav offline routing "
"information, based on OSM data"
msgstr ""
"Monav: Storitev iskanja brez povezave, ki uporablja podatke iz informacij o "
"usmerjanju brez povezave Monav na podlagi podatkov OSM"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gosmore: An offline reverse geocoding service using data from gosmore setup"
msgstr ""
"Gosmore: storitev obratnega geokodiranja brez povezave, ki uporablja podatke "
"iz nastavitev gosmore"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have found your search on the map you can click on its label or its "
"symbol using the &LMB;. After clicking the name of the location on the map a "
"data sheet will appear, like this:"
msgstr ""
"Ko najdete iskalno poizvedbo na zemljevidu, lahko z &LMB; kliknete njeno "
"oznako ali simbol. Ko kliknete ime lokacije na zemljevidu, se prikaže "
"podatkovni list, kot je ta:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&marble; Data Sheet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&marble; Podatkovni list</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&marble; Data Sheet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&marble; Podatkovni list</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the first tab of the dialog some very basic data is provided, like the "
"name, coordinates and flag of the country the place belongs to. In addition, "
"population numbers for cities get shown, as well as the elevation for "
"mountains. If your computer is connected to the Internet and if you're "
"online, &marble; will try to connect to the popular Internet encyclopedia "
"<quote>Wikipedia</quote>. If a matching Wikipedia article is available "
"&marble; will display it on the data sheet."
msgstr ""
"Na prvem zavihku pogovornega okna so na voljo nekateri zelo osnovni podatki, "
"kot so ime, koordinate in zastava države, ki ji kraj pripada. Poleg tega je "
"prikazano število prebivalcev mest in višina gora. Če je vaš računalnik "
"povezan z internetom in če ste povezani, se bo &marble; poskušal povezati s "
"priljubljeno internetno enciklopedijo <quote>Wikipedia</quote>. Če je na "
"voljo ujemajoči se članek iz Wikipedije ga bo &marble; prikazal na "
"podatkovnem listu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The additional data sources can be enabled using <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Online services</guisubmenu></menuchoice> submenu. For "
"example, you should mark <guimenuitem>Wikipedia</guimenuitem> menu item to "
"see Wikipedia articles."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne vire podatkov je mogoče omogočiti s podmenijem "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Spletne storitve</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Na primer, označite element menija "
"<guimenuitem>Wikipedia</guimenuitem>, če si želite ogledati članke v "
"Wikipediji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find your way with &marble;"
msgstr "Poiščite svojo pot z &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides searching for places, &marble; can display possible routes between "
"two or more of them. Do you want to plan a bicycle tour in the nearby wood? "
"Need driving instructions to get to an address in a foreign city? Select the "
"<guilabel>Routing</guilabel> tab on the top of &marble;'s toolbox to start "
"planning your trip."
msgstr ""
"Poleg iskanja krajev, &marble; lahko prikaže možne poti med dvema ali več "
"kraji. Ali želite načrtovati kolesarsko turo po bližnjem gozdu? Potrebujete "
"navodila za vožnjo, da pridete do naslova v tujem mestu? Izberite zavihek "
"<guilabel>Načrtovanje poti</guilabel> na vrhu orodjarne &marble;, da začnete "
"načrtovati potovanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a new Route"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje nove poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Routing</guilabel> tab you'll see two green icons "
"<guibutton>A</guibutton> and <guibutton>B</guibutton>. Enter the start "
"address in the input field next to the <guibutton>A</guibutton> button, the "
"route start input field. Press &Enter; or press the <guibutton>Search</"
"guibutton> button to find matching placemarks. A small progress animation "
"will shorten your waiting time while the search is running. Using the search "
"term <quote>Weavers Lane, London</quote>, the result will look similar to "
"the screenshot below:"
msgstr ""
"Na zavihku <guilabel>Usmerjanje</guilabel> boste videli dve zeleni ikoni "
"<guibutton>A</guibutton> in <guibutton>B</guibutton>. Vnesite začetni naslov "
"v polje za vnos poleg gumba <guibutton>A</guibutton>, polje za vnos začetka "
"poti. Pritisnite &Enter; ali pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Išči</guibutton>, da "
"poiščete ujemajoče se oznake položaja. Majhna animacija napredka bo "
"skrajšala vaš čakalni čas med iskanjem. Če uporabite iskalni izraz "
"<quote>Weavers Lane, London</quote>, bo rezultat podoben spodnjemu posnetku "
"zaslona:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; address search"
msgstr "&marble; iskanje po naslovu"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Searching Addresses"
msgstr "&marble; Iskanje naslovov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Matching placemarks line up in the list below the input fields. They are "
"also shown in the map. The first result is automatically selected as the "
"route start. In the map, this position is indicated using the same "
"<guiicon>A</guiicon> icon as the button next to the route start input field. "
"If the first result is not your desired route start, click on any other "
"result to make that the new start position. You can either click on it in "
"the result list or on its icon in the map to achieve that. The currently "
"chosen route start is always indicated using the <guiicon>A</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Ujemajoče se oznake položaja se vrstijo na seznamu pod polji za vnos. "
"Prikazane so tudi na zemljevidu. Prvi rezultat je samodejno izbran kot "
"začetek poti. Na zemljevidu je ta položaj označen z isto ikono <guiicon>A</"
"guiicon> kot gumb poleg vnosnega polja za začetek poti. Če prvi rezultat ni "
"vaš želeni začetek poti, kliknite kateri koli drug rezultat, da bo ta nov "
"začetni položaj. Lahko ga kliknete na seznamu rezultatov ali njegovo ikono "
"na zemljevidu, da to dosežete. Trenutno izbrani začetek poti je vedno "
"označen z ikono <guiicon>A</guiicon>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the route start at hand, let's move on to enter the destination of our "
"trip. The procedure is the same: Enter the destination address in the input "
"field next to the <guibutton>B</guibutton> button, press &Enter; and select "
"the desired item among the result list."
msgstr ""
"Ko je začetek poti blizu, pojdimo naprej in vnesemo cilj našega potovanja. "
"Postopek je enak: Vnesite ciljni naslov v vnosno polje poleg gumba "
"<guibutton>B</guibutton>, pritisnite &Enter; in med seznamom rezultatov "
"izberite želeni element."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Did you notice that the <guilabel>Search</guilabel> button is now gone and "
"replaced by a <guilabel>Get Directions</guilabel> button? &marble; is "
"signalizing that all information needed to calculate a route has been "
"entered correctly. Press the <guilabel>Get Directions</guilabel> button to "
"retrieve a suitable route now. If your destination search term is <quote>Sun "
"Walk, London</quote>, the result will resemble this screenshot:"
msgstr ""
"Ali ste opazili, da gumba <guilabel>Išči</guilabel> ni več in ga je "
"nadomestil gumb <guilabel>Pridobi navodila</guilabel>? &marble; signalizira, "
"da so vse informacije, potrebne za izračun poti, pravilno vnesene. "
"Pritisnite gumb <guilabel>Pridobi navodila</guilabel>, da zdaj pridobite "
"ustrezno pot. Če je vaš ciljni iskalni izraz <quote>Sun Walk, London</"
"quote>, bo rezultat podoben temu posnetku zaslona:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; route result"
msgstr "&marble; rezultat poti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Displaying a Route"
msgstr "&marble; Prikaz poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the start (or destination) position is already visible on the screen, you "
"may find it more convenient to select it directly in the map. To do that, "
"press the <guibutton>A</guibutton> (or <guibutton>B</guibutton>) button next "
"to the input field. Select <guilabel>From Map</guilabel> in the upcoming "
"menu. Once pressed, the map input mode is activated: The next click on a "
"position in the map will become the start (or end) of your trip. The mouse "
"cursor turns into a cross to ease an accurate selection. The selected "
"position will be included in the route and marked in the map. To abort the "
"selection, either press the button again or press &Esc;."
msgstr ""
"Če je začetni (ali ciljni) položaj že viden na zaslonu, bo morda bolj "
"priročno, da ga izberete neposredno na zemljevidu. Če želite to narediti, "
"pritisnite gumb <guibutton>A</guibutton> (ali <guibutton>B</guibutton>) "
"poleg vnosnega polja. V prihajajočem meniju izberite <guilabel>Z zemljevida</"
"guilabel>. Ko ga pritisnete, se aktivira način vnosa zemljevida: Naslednji "
"klik na položaj na zemljevidu bo postal začetek (ali konec) vašega "
"potovanja. Kazalec miške se spremeni v križec, da olajša natančno izbiro. "
"Izbrana pozicija bo vključena v pot in označena na zemljevidu. Če želite "
"prekiniti izbiro, ponovno pritisnite gumb ali pritisnite &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An alternative selection of the route start and destination is provided via "
"the context menu of the map: Click with the &RMB; on the desired location "
"and select <guilabel>Directions from here</guilabel> or <guilabel>Directions "
"to here</guilabel>, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Alternativna izbira začetka in cilja poti je na voljo prek kontekstnega "
"menija zemljevida: Kliknite z &RMB; na želeni lokaciji in izberite "
"<guilabel>Navodila od tukaj</guilabel> oziroma <guilabel>Navodila do sem</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Route Profiles"
msgstr "Profili poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Which route to choose depends on the type of vehicle you plan to use (if "
"any). You can tell &marble; about this and other preferences using route "
"profiles. Each profile contains the settings for a certain routing scenario. "
"On the first start, &marble; creates four common profiles for you: "
"<guilabel>Car (fastest)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Car (shortest)</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Bike</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Pedestrian</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Katero pot izbrati je odvisno od vrste vozila, ki ga nameravate uporabiti "
"(če obstaja). Lahko rečete &marble; o tem in drugih nastavitvah z uporabo "
"profilov poti. Vsak profil vsebuje nastavitve za določen scenarij "
"usmerjanja. Ob prvem zagonu je &marble; za vas ustvari štiri običajne "
"profile: <guilabel>Avto (najhitrejši)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Avto "
"(najkrajši)</guilabel>, <guilabel>Kolo</guilabel> in <guilabel>Pešec</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The examples in the previous sections used the <guilabel>Car (fastest)</"
"guilabel> profile. Let's revisit the last route with a different profile: "
"Select the <guilabel>Pedestrian</guilabel> option in the <guilabel>Profile</"
"guilabel> combo box. The route now looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"V primerih v prejšnjih razdelkih je bil uporabljen profil <guilabel>Avto "
"(najhitrejši)</guilabel>. Oglejmo si zadnjo pot z drugim profilom: Izberite "
"možnost <guilabel>Pešec</guilabel> v kombiniranem polju <guilabel>Profil</"
"guilabel>. Pot je zdaj videti takole:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; pedestrian routing"
msgstr "&marble; usmerjanje za pešce"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Pedestrian routing"
msgstr "&marble; Usmerjanje za pešce"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The proposed route has become shorter because footways are now also included "
"when calculating the best route."
msgstr ""
"Predlagana pot je postala krajša, ker so zdaj pri izračunu najboljše poti "
"vključene tudi pešpoti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to tweak one of the default profiles further, select it in the "
"<guilabel>Profile</guilabel> combo box and click on the <guilabel>Configure</"
"guilabel> link. A new window opens."
msgstr ""
"Če želite enega od privzetih profilov dodatno prilagoditi, ga izberite v "
"kombiniranem polju <guilabel>Profil</guilabel> in kliknite povezavo "
"<guilabel>Konfiguriraj</guilabel>. Odpre se novo okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; route profile configuration"
msgstr "&marble; konfiguracijo profila poti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Route Profile configuration"
msgstr "&marble; Konfiguracija profila poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left side lets you configure which routing backends are queried for "
"routes. Eight or more backends are supported by &marble;, some working "
"online and the other ones working offline. Online routing requires an "
"Internet connection to query a route. Offline routing works without an "
"Internet connection, but requires you to download and install offline "
"routing maps in advance. The supported routing backends are"
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani lahko konfigurirate, katera zaledja usmerjanja so poizvedena "
"za pot. Osem ali več ozadij podpira &marble;, nekateri delujejo na spletu, "
"drugi pa brez povezave. Spletno usmerjanje zahteva internetno povezavo za "
"iskanje poti. Usmerjanje brez povezave deluje brez internetne povezave, "
"vendar zahteva, da vnaprej prenesete in namestite zemljevide za usmerjanje "
"brez povezave. Podprta zaledja usmerjanja so"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"CycleStreets: Bicycle routing for the United Kingdom using cyclestreets.net"
msgstr ""
"CycleStreets: kolesarske poti za Združeno kraljestvo z uporabo cyclestreets."
"net"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gosmore: An offline router that also serves as the backend for the Yours "
"online router"
msgstr ""
"Gosmore: usmerjevalnik brez povezave, ki služi tudi kot zaledje za spletni "
"usmerjevalnik Yours"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"MapQuest: An online router which provides advanced turn-by-turn instructions"
msgstr ""
"MapQuest: spletni usmerjevalnik, ki ponuja napredna navodila zavoj za zavojem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An AppKey is required for MapQuest routing to work. You can register the "
"AppKey <ulink url=\"https://developer.mapquest.com/plan_purchase/steps/"
"business_edition/business_edition_free/register\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za delovanje MapQuest usmerjanja je potreben AppKey. AppKey lahko "
"registrirate <ulink url=\"https://developer.mapquest.com/plan_purchase/steps/"
"business_edition/business_edition_free/register\">tukaj</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Monav: An offline router that is very fast even when calculating very large "
"routes"
msgstr ""
"Monav: Usmerjevalnik brez povezave, ki je zelo hiter tudi pri izračunu zelo "
"velikih poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OSRM: An online router that is very fast even when calculating very large "
"routes"
msgstr ""
"OSRM: spletni usmerjevalnik, ki je zelo hiter tudi pri izračunu zelo velikih "
"poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OpenRouteService: An online router that also generates driving instructions, "
"limited to Europe"
msgstr ""
"OpenRouteService: spletni usmerjevalnik, ki ustvarja tudi navodila za "
"vožnjo, omejen na Evropo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routino: An offline router with a very flexible configuration"
msgstr ""
"Routino: Usmerjevalnik brez povezave z zelo prilagodljivo konfiguracijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yours: An online router that operates world-wide, but lacks driving "
"instructions"
msgstr ""
"Vaš: spletni usmerjevalnik, ki deluje po vsem svetu, vendar nima navodil za "
"vožnjo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you select and enable a routing backend on the left to include it in "
"routing queries, you can modify its settings on the right side. The settings "
"are specific to each backend."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete in omogočite zaledje usmerjanja na levi, da ga vključite v "
"poizvedbe za usmerjanje, lahko spremenite njegove nastavitve na desni "
"strani. Nastavitve so specifične za vsako zaledje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides configuring the four default profiles, you can add new profiles and "
"remove existing ones in the &marble; settings in the <guilabel>Routing</"
"guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Poleg konfiguracije štirih privzetih profilov lahko dodate nove profile in "
"odstranite obstoječe v mapi &marble; nastavitve na strani "
"<guilabel>Usmerjanje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjusting Routes"
msgstr "Prilagajanje poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; let's you modify several aspects of the route for fine-tuning: "
"Change route options, insert via points, move or remove existing points. The "
"modification of route options has been discussed in the previous section "
"already; we'll concentrate on point management now."
msgstr ""
"&marble; spremenite več vidikov poti za natančno nastavitev: spremenite "
"možnosti poti, vstavite vmesne točke, premaknite ali odstranite obstoječe "
"točke. Spreminjanje možnosti poti je bilo že obravnavano v prejšnjem "
"razdelku; zdaj se bomo osredotočili na upravljanje točk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserting via points is done by drag-and-drop in the map. Every time you "
"move the mouse pointer above any part of the route (except above existing "
"trip points), a green flag icon appears to indicate that it is possible to "
"insert a via point. To start the insert operation, click with the &LMB;. "
"Move the mouse pointer to the desired new position while keeping the &LMB; "
"pressed. Blue lines from the neighboring via points to the new position will "
"appear:"
msgstr ""
"Vstavljanje vmesnih točk se izvede s povleci in spusti na zemljevid. Vsakič, "
"ko premaknete kazalec miške nad kateri koli del poti (razen nad obstoječe "
"točke potovanja), se prikaže ikona zelene zastavice, ki označuje, da je "
"možno vstaviti vmesno točko. Za začetek operacije vstavljanja kliknite z "
"&LMB;. Premaknite kazalec miške na želeni nov položaj, pri tem pa držite "
"&LMB; stisnjen. Prikazale se bodo modre črte od sosednjih vmesnih točk do "
"novega položaja:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; route adding via points"
msgstr "&marble; dodajanje vmesnih točk poti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Inserting a via point"
msgstr "&marble; Vstavljanje vmesne točke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The new via point will be inserted between the existing neighbor via points "
"once you release the &LMB;. At the same time the existing route is painted "
"dotted to indicate that it contains outdated information. In the background, "
"a new route is prepared which will replace the outdated one automatically."
msgstr ""
"Nova vmesna točka bo vstavljena med obstoječe sosednje vmesne točke, ko "
"spustite &LMB;. Hkrati je obstoječa pot pobarvana s pikami, kar pomeni, da "
"vsebuje zastarele informacije. V ozadju se pripravlja nova pot, ki bo "
"samodejno nadomestila zastarelo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is also possible to add via points before the start or after the end of "
"the route. To do that, follow the instructions above for inserting a new via "
"point, but press &Ctrl; while moving the mouse. One blue line from the start "
"or the end of the route appears. Its origin indicates where the new via "
"point will be appended."
msgstr ""
"Vmesne točke je mogoče dodati tudi pred začetkom ali po koncu poti. Če "
"želite to narediti, sledite zgornjim navodilom za vstavljanje nove vmesne "
"točke, vendar pritisnite &Ctrl; med premikanjem miške. Prikaže se ena modra "
"črta od začetka ali konca poti. Njegov izvor nakazuje, kam bo dodana nova "
"vmesna točka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Existing via points can be moved freely across the map. Move the mouse "
"pointer above a via point and drag it to its new location. Once released, "
"the route will be updated automatically."
msgstr ""
"Obstoječe vmesne točke lahko prosto premikate po zemljevidu. Premaknite "
"kazalec miške nad vmesno točko in jo povlecite na novo lokacijo. Po "
"sprostitvi se pot samodejno posodobi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To exclude via points from the route, remove them. This can be done using "
"either the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button next to the via point input "
"field or by clicking with the &RMB; on the via point in the map. In the "
"context menu, choose <guimenuitem>Remove this Destination</guimenuitem>. To "
"start an entirely new route, remove all via points."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vmesne točke izključiti iz poti, jih odstranite. To lahko storite "
"z gumbom <guibutton>Odstrani</guibutton> poleg polja za vnos vmesne točke "
"ali s klikom &RMB; na vmesni točki na zemljevidu. V kontekstnem meniju "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Odstrani ta cilj</guimenuitem>. Če želite začeti "
"povsem novo pot, odstranite vse vmesne točke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading, Saving and Exporting Routes"
msgstr "Nalaganje, shranjevanje in izvoz poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can save routes in <acronym>kml</acronym> (Keyhole Markup Language) "
"format and load them again at a later point - on the same computer or a "
"different device running &marble;, or share them with your friends or other "
"applications which are able to read kml files (like <application>Google "
"Earth</application>). To save a route to a <literal role=\"extension\">.kml</"
"literal> file, press the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button on the bottom of "
"the routing tab. The upcoming save dialog allows you to choose a file name "
"to save the route to. Similarly loading a route is initiated with the "
"<guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the bottom of the routing tab. Select "
"the <literal role=\"extension\">.kml</literal> route file to open in the "
"upcoming open dialog and &marble; loads the route from it."
msgstr ""
"Poti lahko shranite v formatu <acronym>kml</acronym> (Keyhole Markup "
"Language) in jih znova naložite pozneje – v istem računalniku ali drugi "
"napravi, v kateri se izvaja &marble;, ali pa jih delite s prijatelji ali "
"drugimi aplikacijami, ki lahko berejo datoteke kml (kot je "
"<application>Google Earth</application>). Če želite pot shraniti v datoteko "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.kml</literal>, pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> na dnu zavihka za usmerjanje. Prihajajoče "
"pogovorno okno za shranjevanje vam omogoča, da izberete ime datoteke, v "
"katero želite shraniti pot. Podobno se nalaganje poti začne z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Odpri</guibutton> na dnu zavihka za usmerjanje. Izberite datoteko "
"poti <literal role=\"extension\">.kml</literal>, ki jo želite odpreti v "
"prihajajočem odprtem pogovornem oknu in &marble; iz njega naloži pot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Routes planned in &marble; can be used in other applications or navigation "
"devices which support <acronym>gpx</acronym> (GPS eXchange Format) or "
"equivalent formats. If your navigation device does not support <acronym>gpx</"
"acronym> directly, you can use a conversion utility like <command>gpsbabel</"
"command> to convert a <acronym>gpx</acronym> file exported by &marble; to a "
"suitable format. The export of a route in &marble; is initiated from the "
"routing context menu in the map. Click with the &RMB; on any point of the "
"route in the map. In the context menu that appears, choose "
"<guimenuitem>Export Route...</guimenuitem>:"
msgstr ""
"Poti, načrtovane v &marble; se lahko uporablja v drugih aplikacijah ali "
"navigacijskih napravah, ki podpirajo <acronym>gpx</acronym> (GPS eXchange "
"Format) ali enakovredne formate. Če vaša navigacijska naprava ne podpira "
"neposredno <acronym>gpx</acronym>, lahko uporabite pripomoček za pretvorbo, "
"kot je <command>gpsbabel</command>, da pretvorite datoteko <acronym>gpx</"
"acronym>, ki jo izvozi &marble; v primerno obliko. Izvoz poti v &marble; se "
"sproži iz kontekstnega menija usmerjanja na zemljevidu. Kliknite z &RMB; na "
"kateri koli točki poti na zemljevidu. V kontekstnem meniju, ki se prikaže, "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Izvozi pot...</guimenuitem>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; route export"
msgstr "&marble; izvoz poti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Exporting a Route"
msgstr "&marble; Izvoz poti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the desired filename in the upcoming save dialog. The filename "
"extension should be <literal role=\"extension\">gpx</literal> to store in "
"<acronym>gpx</acronym> format or <literal role=\"extension\">kml</literal> "
"to store in <acronym>kml</acronym> (Keyhole Markup Language) format. Note "
"that the internal format of &marble; is <acronym>kml</acronym>; in doubt "
"save routes as <acronym>kml</acronym> and only use <acronym>gpx</acronym> to "
"share routes with other applications that are not capable of reading "
"<acronym>kml</acronym> files."
msgstr ""
"V prihajajoče pogovorno okno za shranjevanje vnesite želeno ime datoteke. "
"Pripona imena datoteke mora biti <literal role=\"extension\">gpx</literal> "
"za shranjevanje v formatu <acronym>gpx</acronym> ali <literal role="
"\"extension\">kml</literal> za shranjevanje v <acronym> format kml</acronym> "
"(keyhole markup language). Upoštevajte, da notranji format &marble; je "
"<acronym>kml</acronym>; v dvomih shranite poti kot <acronym>kml</acronym> in "
"uporabite samo <acronym>gpx</acronym> za skupno rabo poti z drugimi "
"aplikacijami, ki ne morejo brati datotek <acronym>kml</acronym>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Measuring distances with &marble;"
msgstr "Merjenje razdalj z &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned already &marble; always displays a dynamic scale bar on the "
"lower left to estimate distances on the map. Together with the windrose in "
"the top right corner these overlays are provided for better orientation. But "
"there's more: &marble; allows you to measure distances between two or more "
"points on earth. To do so click the respective points in correct order on "
"the globe using the &RMB;. On each click a popup menu will appear which "
"allows you to add a measure point (<guimenuitem>Add Measure Point</"
"guimenuitem>) or to remove all measure points altogether "
"(<guimenuitem>Remove Measure Points</guimenuitem>):"
msgstr ""
"Kot že omenjeno &marble; vedno prikaže dinamično vrstico merila spodaj levo "
"za oceno razdalj na zemljevidu. Skupaj z rožo vetrov v zgornjem desnem kotu "
"so ti prekrivni elementi za boljšo orientacijo. Vendar je še več: &marble; "
"omogoča merjenje razdalj med dvema ali več točkami na zemlji. To storite "
"tako, da z &RMB; kliknete ustrezne točke na globusu v pravilnem vrstnem "
"redu. Ob vsakem kliku se prikaže pojavni meni, ki vam omogoča dodajanje "
"merilne točke (<guimenuitem>Dodaj merilno točko</guimenuitem>) ali popolno "
"odstranitev vseh merilnih točk (<guimenuitem>Odstrani merilne točke</"
"guimenuitem>):"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; measuring"
msgstr "&marble; merjenje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; measuring distances"
msgstr "&marble; merjenje razdalj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have added at least two measure points, the total distance will be "
"displayed in the top left corner of the map. &marble; will assume a "
"spherical earth for all measurements which should be accurate enough for "
"most cases."
msgstr ""
"Ko dodate vsaj dve merilni točki, bo skupna razdalja prikazana v zgornjem "
"levem kotu zemljevida. &marble; bo za vse meritve predpostavil sferično "
"zemljo, ki bi morala biti dovolj natančna za večino primerov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displaying of distances and bearings for the measured segments can be "
"configured using <link linkend=\"measure-tool-config\">Measure Tool "
"configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz razdalj in smeri za izmerjene segmente lahko konfigurirate z <link "
"linkend=\"measure-tool-config\">konfiguracijskim pogovornim oknom orodja za "
"merjenje</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Download Map Regions"
msgstr "Prenesite zemljevid regij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pre-installed with a set of maps, &marble; is ready to use. When you zoom in "
"at places, more detailed parts of the current map theme are downloaded in "
"the background. This works excellent whenever an Internet connection is "
"available. What to do, however, when traveling to a foreign city where no "
"constant Internet connection is available to download maps? Plan ahead and "
"download those map regions you are going to use."
msgstr ""
"Vnaprej nameščen z naborom zemljevidov, &marble; je pripravljen za uporabo. "
"Ko na mestih povečate, se v ozadju prenesejo podrobnejši deli trenutne teme "
"zemljevida. To deluje odlično, kadar koli je na voljo internetna povezava. "
"Kaj pa storiti, ko potujete v tuje mesto, kjer ni na voljo stalne internetne "
"povezave za prenos zemljevidov? Načrtujte vnaprej in prenesite tiste "
"zemljevide regij, ki jih boste uporabljali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To understand what needs to be downloaded to display certain parts of the "
"map offline, let's briefly look into the concept of tiles which &marble; "
"uses internally. A tile is an image which corresponds to a certain part of "
"the map. Tiles are arranged by &marble; next to each other to form the map "
"image that is displayed to you. Depending on the selected projection mode, "
"tiles are arranged to form a rectangle (Flat Map Projection, left) or a "
"sphere (Globe Projection, right):"
msgstr ""
"Da bi razumeli, kaj je treba prenesti za prikaz določenih delov zemljevida "
"brez povezave, si na kratko poglejmo koncept ploščic, ki &marble; uporablja "
"interno. Ploščica je slika, ki ustreza določenemu delu zemljevida. Ploščice "
"razporedi &marble; eni poleg druge, da tvorijo sliko zemljevida, ki se vam "
"prikaže. Odvisno od izbranega načina projekcije so ploščice razporejene "
"tako, da tvorijo pravokotnik (ravna projekcija zemljevida, levo) ali kroglo "
"(globusna projekcija, desno):"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; projections"
msgstr "&marble; projekcije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tiles at Level 1 in Flat Map (left) and Globe Projection (right)"
msgstr ""
"Ploščice na ravni 1 v zemljevidu ploskve (levo) in projekciji globusa (desno)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Zooming in at this view, more details need to be displayed. The tiles shown "
"in the two screenshots above are too coarse then; &marble; automatically "
"recognizes this and changes to the next tile level where images provide more "
"details. This keeps going: The more you zoom in, the higher the tile level. "
"The following sketch illustrates the different number of tiles (colored) "
"corresponding to the same map region at different tile levels:"
msgstr ""
"Če povečate ta pogled, je treba prikazati več podrobnosti. Ploščice, "
"prikazane na zgornjih dveh posnetkih zaslona, so torej pregrobe; &marble; "
"samodejno prepozna to in preklopi na naslednjo raven ploščic, kjer slike "
"zagotavljajo več podrobnosti. To se nadaljuje: bolj ko povečate, višja je "
"raven ploščic. Naslednja skica ponazarja različno število ploščic (barvnih), "
"ki ustrezajo isti regiji zemljevida na različnih ravneh ploščic:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; tile levels"
msgstr "&marble; ravni ploščic"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "Different Tile Levels in &marble;"
msgstr "Različne ravni ploščic v &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When downloading a map region for offline usage, you need to download all "
"tiles in the desired region for all tile levels you plan to use. Because of "
"the connection between tile levels and zoom levels, you can think of it as "
"downloading all tiles in the zoom levels you plan to use."
msgstr ""
"Ko prenašate regijo zemljevida za uporabo brez povezave, morate prenesti vse "
"ploščice v želeni regiji za vse ravni ploščic, ki jih nameravate uporabiti. "
"Zaradi povezave med stopnjami ploščic in stopnjami povečave si lahko to "
"predstavljate kot prenos vseh ploščic v stopnjah povečave, ki jih nameravate "
"uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To accomplish this for a certain region, make that region visible in the "
"screen by zooming and moving the Globe. Now select the "
"<menuchoice><guilabel>File</guilabel> <guilabel>Download Region...</"
"guilabel></menuchoice> menu item to open the <guilabel>Download Region</"
"guilabel> dialog. Keep the <guilabel>Visible region</guilabel> option "
"selected to download those tiles that correspond to the map region visible "
"in the screen. Next, select the <guilabel>Tile level range:</guilabel> (zoom "
"range) you wish to download. The first field corresponds to the smallest, "
"the second field corresponds to the largest tile level that will be "
"downloaded. Tile levels in between will be downloaded as well. &marble; "
"shows how many tiles (images) need to be downloaded and updates this number "
"whenever you change the region or tile level range."
msgstr ""
"Če želite to doseči za določeno regijo, naredite to regijo vidno na zaslonu "
"s povečavo in premikanjem globusa. Sedaj izberite element menija "
"<menuchoice><guilabel>Datoteka</guilabel> <guilabel>Prenos regije...</"
"guilabel></menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno <guilabel>Prenos regije</"
"guilabel>. Pustite izbrano možnost <guilabel>Vidna regija</guilabel>, da "
"prenesete tiste ploščice, ki ustrezajo regiji zemljevida, vidni na zaslonu. "
"Nato izberite <guilabel>Razpon ravni ploščice:</guilabel> (razpon povečave), "
"ki ga želite prenesti. Prvo polje ustreza najmanjšemu, drugo polje ustreza "
"največji stopnji ploščice, ki bo prenesena. Prenesene bodo tudi vmesne ravni "
"ploščic. &marble; prikazuje, koliko ploščic (slik) je treba prenesti, in to "
"številko posodobi vsakič, ko spremenite regijo ali obseg ravni ploščic."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Download Region dialog"
msgstr "&marble; Prenos pogovornega okna Regija"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble;'s Download Region dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za prenos območja &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tile level corresponding to the current zoom level is shown in the "
"status bar on the bottom. Please note that you may have to configure "
"&marble; to show that information: Click with the &RMB; on the status bar "
"and select <guilabel>Show Tile Zoom Level</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Raven ploščice, ki ustreza trenutni stopnji povečave, je prikazana v vrstici "
"stanja na dnu. Upoštevajte, da boste morda morali konfigurirati &marble; za "
"prikaz teh informacij: Kliknite z &RMB; v statusni vrstici in izberite "
"<guilabel>Prikaži stopnjo povečave ploščic</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to trigger the map region download. The "
"progress bar of &marble; will show the download progress (if activated)."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da sprožite prenos regije "
"zemljevida. Vrstica napredka &marble; bo prikazal potek prenosa (če je "
"aktiviran)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you do know the coordinates of the map region to download, you can "
"enter them by clicking on the <guilabel>Specify region</guilabel> option. "
"The map region visible in the screen will be ignored in that case."
msgstr ""
"Če poznate koordinate regije zemljevida za prenos, jih lahko vnesete s "
"klikom na možnost <guilabel>Določi regijo</guilabel>. Območje zemljevida, "
"vidno na zaslonu, bo v tem primeru prezrto."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can keep using &marble; while the <guilabel>Download Region</guilabel> "
"dialog is open. This is useful to queue several downloads for different "
"regions or different tile ranges. Just select <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> "
"instead of <guibutton>OK</guibutton> to trigger the map region download."
msgstr ""
"Še naprej lahko uporabljate &marble; ko je odprto pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Prenos regije</guilabel>. To je uporabno za več prenosov v čakalno "
"vrsto za različne regije ali različne obsege ploščic. Samo izberite "
"<guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton> namesto <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, da "
"sprožite prenos regije zemljevida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:450 index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recording a movie with &marble;"
msgstr "Snemanje filma z &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "To record a movie with &marble;, use this function for recording."
msgstr "Če želite posneti film z &marble;, uporabite to funkcijo za snemanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Begin recording from the <menuchoice><shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Record Movie</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to "
"open the <guilabel>Record Movie</guilabel> dialog. You will see a dialog "
"like this:"
msgstr ""
"Začnite snemati z <menuchoice><shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Snemanje Filma</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menijski element za "
"odpiranje pogovornega okna <guilabel>Snemanje filma</guilabel>. Videli boste "
"takšno pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble; Record Movie dialog"
msgstr "&marble; Pogovorno okno za snemanje filma"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid "&marble;'s Record Movie dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za snemanje filma &marble;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Open...</guibutton> button to choose the name and "
"destination folder of the movie. Also you can change the frames per second "
"(FPS) of the movie between 1 and 60."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Odpri...</guibutton>, da izberete ime in ciljno "
"mapo filma. Spremenite lahko tudi število sličic na sekundo (FPS) filma med "
"1 in 60."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When all is set, you can start recording. To start, press the "
"<guibutton>Start</guibutton> button. Once this is done you can zoom and pan "
"around and &marble; will capture a video of your journey across the globe."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vse nastavljeno, lahko začnete snemati. Za začetek pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Začni</guibutton>. Ko je to opravljeno, lahko povečate in se "
"premikate ter &marble; bo posnel videoposnetek vašega potovanja po svetu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To stop recording of the movie and save it, select the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop Recording</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustaviti snemanje filma in ga shraniti, izberite menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi snemanje</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There may appear an error message because avconv or ffmpeg are not "
"installed. Download from <ulink url=\"https://ffmpeg.org/download.html"
"\">ffmpeg's downloads page</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://libav.org/"
"download.html\">avconv's downloads page</ulink> or use packages from your "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"Morda se prikaže sporočilo o napaki, ker nista nameščena avconv ali ffmpeg. "
"Prenesite s <ulink url=\"https://ffmpeg.org/download.html\">strani za "
"prenose ffmpeg</ulink> in <ulink url=\"https://libav.org/download.html"
"\">strani za prenose avconv</ulink> ali uporabite pakete iz vaše "
"distribucije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menus and shortcut keys"
msgstr "Meniji in tipke bližnjic"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Opens</action> a map file."
msgstr "<action>Odpre</action> datoteko zemljevida."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Open Recent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odpri nedavno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a shortcut to open recently opened maps. Clicking on this item opens "
"a list to the side of the menu with several of the most recently opened "
"files. Clicking on a specific file will open it in &marble; - if the file "
"still resides at the same location."
msgstr ""
"To je bližnjica za odpiranje nedavno odprtih zemljevidov. S klikom na ta "
"element se ob strani menija odpre seznam z več nazadnje odprtimi datotekami. "
"Če kliknete določeno datoteko, jo odprete v &marble; - če je datoteka še "
"vedno na istem mestu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Download Maps...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prenos zemljevidov...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Get Hot New Stuff!</guilabel> dialog "
"to download additional maps for &marble;, among others maps for Mars and "
"Venus."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> pogovorno okno <guilabel>Dobi vroče nove stvari!</"
"guilabel> za prenos dodatnih zemljevidov za &marble;, med drugim zemljevidov "
"za Mars in Venero."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Create a New Map...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustvari nov zemljevid...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>&marble; Map Theme Creation Wizard</"
"guilabel> dialog to create a new map using Web Map Service data, your own "
"image file or Open Street Map indexed tiles."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> <guilabel>&marble; Pogovorno okno čarovnika za "
"ustvarjanje teme zemljevida</guilabel> za ustvarjanje novega zemljevida z "
"uporabo podatkov spletne storitve zemljevidov, lastne slikovne datoteke ali "
"indeksiranih ploščic Open Street Map."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Download Region...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Območje prenosa...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Download Region</guilabel> dialog to "
"download map data in different zoom levels for offline usage. See <link "
"linkend=\"download-region\">Download Map Regions</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> pogovorno okno <guilabel>Prenos regije</guilabel> "
"za prenos zemljevidnih podatkov v različnih stopnjah povečave za uporabo "
"brez povezave. Za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend=\"download-region"
"\">Prenos regij zemljevida</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export Map...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvoz zemljevida...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Exports</action> a screenshot of &marble;'s map to an image file."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izvozi</action> posnetek zaslona zemljevida &marble; v slikovno "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Prints</action> a screenshot of &marble;'s map."
msgstr "<action>Natisne</action> posnetek zaslona zemljevida &marble;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a window that shows a preview of the printed map."
msgstr "Odpre okno s predogledom natisnjenega zemljevida."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Work Offline</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delo brez povezave</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected &marble; will no longer download map data from "
"the Internet. The search feature gets restricted to the local database. New "
"routes cannot be retrieved."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost &marble; ne bo več prenašal zemljevidnih podatkov "
"iz interneta. Funkcija iskanja je omejena na lokalno bazo podatkov. Novih "
"poti ni mogoče pridobiti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &marble;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &marble;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy Map</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj zemljevid</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Copies</action> a screenshot of &marble;'s map to the global "
"clipboard."
msgstr ""
"<action>Kopira</action> posnetek zaslona zemljevida &marble; v globalno "
"odložišče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy Coordinates</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj koordinate</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Copies</action> the current coordinates to the global clipboard."
msgstr "<action>Kopira</action> trenutne koordinate v globalno odložišče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Map...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uredi zemljevid...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Allows</action> you to open the current map in the external map "
"editor. The current version supports <application>Potlatch</application> (in "
"a web browser), <application>Merkaartor</application> and <application>JOSM</"
"application> map editors."
msgstr ""
"<action>Omogoča</action>, da odprete trenutni zemljevid v zunanjem "
"urejevalniku zemljevidov. Trenutna različica podpira urejevalnike "
"zemljevidov <application>Potlatch</application> (v spletnem brskalniku), "
"<application>Merkaartor</application> in <application>JOSM</application>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Record Movie</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Posnemi film</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Records</action> a movie with &marble;."
msgstr "<action>Posname</action> film z &marble;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stop Recording</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi snemanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Stops</action> the current recording of movie."
msgstr "<action>Ustavi</action> trenutno snemanje filma."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Current Location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Trenutna lokacija</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle</action> the display of the location page in the left panel. "
"If a GPS device is connected with your computer, &marble; displays longitude "
"and latitude of your current location."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopi</action> prikaz strani lokacije na levi plošči. Če je "
"naprava GPS povezana z vašim računalnikom, &marble; prikaže zemljepisno "
"dolžino in širino vaše trenutne lokacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Crosshairs</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nitni križ</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle</action> the display of a simple crosshair in the center of "
"the map."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopi</action> prikaz preprostega merilnega križca na sredini "
"zemljevida."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Osveži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The currently visible part of the map is downloaded again and refreshed on "
"the screen."
msgstr "Trenutno vidni del zemljevida se znova prenese in osveži na zaslonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Info Boxes</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Informacijska polja</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this submenu you can to lock the position of the infoboxes and show or "
"hide the plugins you have enabled in the <link linkend=\"configplugins"
"\">Plugins</link> page of &marble;s configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"V tem podmeniju lahko zaklenete položaj informacijskih polj in prikažete ali "
"skrijete vtičnike, ki ste jih omogočili na strani <link linkend="
"\"configplugins\">Vtičniki</link> v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu &marble;"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Online Services</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Ogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spletne storitve</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenuitem>Wikipedia</guimenuitem> plugin displays georeferenced "
"Wikipedia articles as an icon on the map. A click onto the icon launches a "
"browser window that displays the referenced site. The data is provided "
"through a webservice via GeoNames.org. Likewise a <guimenuitem>Photos</"
"guimenuitem> plugin currently provides photos via the FlickR photo sharing "
"site."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik <guimenuitem>Wikipedia</guimenuitem> prikaže georeferencirane članke "
"Wikipedije kot ikono na zemljevidu. S klikom na ikono se odpre okno "
"brskalnika, ki prikaže navedeno spletno mesto. Podatki so na voljo prek "
"spletne storitve prek GeoNames.org. Podobno vtičnik <guimenuitem>Photos</"
"guimenuitem> trenutno zagotavlja fotografije prek mesta za skupno rabo "
"fotografij FlickR."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clouds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Oblaki</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show</action> real-time cloud cover. A real-time cloud map that gets "
"updated every 3 hours. It uses GOES, METEOSAT, and GMS satellite imagery "
"downloaded from the Geostationary Satellite Imagery page at Dundee "
"University. Credits: Hari Nair, Xplanet Project."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži</action> oblačnost v realnem času. Zemljevid oblaka v "
"realnem času, ki se posodobi vsake 3 ure. Uporablja satelitske posnetke "
"GOES, METEOSAT in GMS, prenesene s strani Geostationary Satellite Imagery na "
"Univerzi Dundee. Zasluge: Hari Nair, projekt Xplanet."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Atmosphere</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Atmosfera</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Show</action> the diffuse reflection of the atmosphere around the "
"Earth."
msgstr "<action>Pokaže</action> difuzni odboj atmosfere okoli Zemlje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Stars</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zvezde</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Show</action> the star map as seen from the Solar System."
msgstr "<action>Prikaže</action> zvezdni zemljevid, kot je viden iz Osončja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sun Control...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nadzor sonca...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Sun Control</guilabel> where you can "
"set the <guilabel>Sun Shading</guilabel> and center the map on subsolar "
"point position."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> <guilabel>nadzor Sonca</guilabel>, kjer lahko "
"nastavite <guilabel>Sončno senčenje</guilabel> in centrirate zemljevid na "
"položaj podsončne točke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Time Control...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nadzor časa...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Time Control</guilabel> dialog where "
"you can set date and time and the simulation time speed."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> pogovorno okno <guilabel>Nadzor časa</guilabel>, "
"kjer lahko nastavite datum in čas ter časovno hitrost simulacije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Eclipses in <replaceable>year</"
"replaceable></guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Ogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Mrki v <replaceable>letu</replaceable></"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the list of the eclipses for the year chosen using "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Browse Eclipses...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> seznam mrkov za leto, izbrano z menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prebrskaj po mrkih...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:700 index.docbook:709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item will be shown only when <link linkend=\"eclipsesplugin"
"\">Eclipses</link> plugin is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ta element menija bo prikazan le, če je omogočen vtičnik <link linkend="
"\"eclipsesplugin\">Eclipse</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:704
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Browse Eclipses...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Ogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prebrskaj Eclipse...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Displays</action> the <guilabel>Eclipse Browser</guilabel> dialog "
"where you can set the year to show eclipses for, open plugin settings "
"dialog, view data on eclipse start, end, type and magnitude. Choose some "
"eclipse item from the list and press the <guibutton>Go To Selected Eclipse</"
"guibutton> to view the location of the eclipse on the globe."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže</action> pogovorno okno <guilabel>Eclipse Browser</"
"guilabel>, kjer lahko nastavite leto za prikaz mrkov, odprete pogovorno okno "
"z nastavitvami vtičnika, si ogledate podatke o začetku, koncu, vrsti in "
"magnitudi mrkov. Izberite nekaj elementov mrka s seznama in pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Pojdi na izbrani mrk</guibutton>, da si ogledate lokacijo mrka na "
"globusu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "Meni z zaznamki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Bookmark...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj zaznamek...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open the <guilabel>Edit Bookmark</guilabel> dialog</action> to "
"manage a bookmark."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odprite pogovorno okno <guilabel>Urejanje zaznamka</guilabel></"
"action> za upravljanje zaznamka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži zaznamke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A check box for <action>enable the bookmarks visualization on the map.</"
"action>"
msgstr ""
"Potrditveno polje za <action>omogoči vizualizacijo zaznamkov na zemljevidu.</"
"action>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Home Location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavi domačo lokacijo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the current position as your house."
msgstr "Nastavite trenutni položaj kot svojo hišo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Manage Bookmarks...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Upravljanje zaznamkov...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Open the <guilabel>Manage Bookmarks</guilabel> dialog</action> to "
"manage all bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odprite pogovorno okno <guilabel>Upravljanje zaznamkov</guilabel></"
"action> za upravljanje vseh zaznamkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Default</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Privzeto</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid "This submenu shows your default locations."
msgstr "Ta podmeni prikazuje vaše privzete lokacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži orodno vrstico</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle</action> the display of the toolbar."
msgstr "<action>Preklop</action> prikaza orodne vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži vrstico stanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle</action> the display of the status bar."
msgstr "<action>Preklopi</action> prikaz statusne vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Panels</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Plošče</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:777
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Toggle</action> the display of the &marble; panels."
msgstr "<action>Preklopi</action> prikaz plošče &marble;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make &marble; hide all panels or show them by selecting the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Panels</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Hide All Panels/Show All Panels</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item or pressing <keycap>F9</keycap> key on your keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Lahko naredite &marble; skrijte vse plošče ali jih pokažite tako, da "
"izberete menijski element <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Plošče</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Skrij vse plošče/Prikaži vse "
"plošče</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali pritisnete Tipko <keycap>F9</keycap> "
"na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View Size</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Velikost pogleda</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Switches between various sizes of &marble; map area.</action> You "
"can choose one of the sizes that are suitable for capturing frames for "
"screencast or keep &marble; map area resizable (<guimenuitem>Default "
"(resizable)</guimenuitem> item)."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopi med različnimi velikostmi &marble; območje zemljevida.</"
"action> Izberete lahko eno od velikosti, ki so primerne za zajem okvirjev za "
"predvajanje zaslona ali ohranite &marble; območje zemljevida, ki ga je "
"mogoče spremeniti v velikosti (element <guimenuitem>Privzeto (spremenljivo)</"
"guimenuitem>)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Full Screen "
"Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Celozaslonski način</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Switches between normal view and full screen view.</action> In full "
"screen view, the titlebar is hidden and the actual application window is "
"resized to the entire screen."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopi med običajnim pogledom in celozaslonskim pogledom.</action> "
"V celozaslonskem pogledu je naslovna vrstica skrita in velikost dejanskega "
"okna aplikacije je spremenjena na celoten zaslon."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &marble; Virtual Globe..."
"</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &marble; Virtualni "
"globus...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Display</action> the <link linkend=\"configure\">&marble; "
"configuration</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaži</action> <link linkend=\"configure\">&marble; "
"konfiguracijsko</link> pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for more "
"information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&marble; ima skupno &kde; Element menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več "
"informacij preberite razdelek o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">meniju Pomoč</ulink> programa &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &marble;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &marble;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Configuration"
msgstr "Ogled konfiguracije"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The View configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo pogleda</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The View configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo pogleda</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid "Distance:"
msgstr "Razdalja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The unit that gets used to measure altitude, lengths and distances (&eg; km, "
"mi, ft)."
msgstr ""
"Enota, ki se uporablja za merjenje nadmorske višine, dolžin in razdalj (eg; "
"km, mi, ft)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid "Angle:"
msgstr "Kot:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the notation of angles in coordinates: By default the Degree-"
"Minute-Second notation (&eg; 54°30'00\" ) gets used. As an alternative you "
"can choose decimal degrees (&eg; 54.5°)."
msgstr ""
"Določa zapis kotov v koordinatah: privzeto se uporabi zapis stopinja-minuta-"
"sekunda (&eg; 54°30'00\" ). Kot alternativo lahko izberete decimalne "
"stopinje (&eg; 54,5°)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid "Still image:"
msgstr "Slika:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the map quality that gets displayed while there is no user input. "
"Usually this allows for high map quality as speed is no concern."
msgstr ""
"Določa kakovost zemljevida, ki se prikaže, ko ni vnosa uporabnika. Običajno "
"to omogoča visoko kakovost zemljevida, saj hitrost ni pomembna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:848
#, no-c-format
msgid "During animations:"
msgstr "Med animacijami:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifies the map quality that gets displayed during map animations (&eg; "
"while dragging the globe). Especially on slow machines it is advisable to "
"set this option to <guilabel>Low Quality</guilabel> as this will give better "
"speed."
msgstr ""
"Določa kakovost zemljevida, ki se prikaže med animacijami zemljevida (&eg;. "
"med vlečenjem globusa). Zlasti na počasnih strojih je priporočljivo, da to "
"možnost nastavite na <guilabel>Nizka kakovost</guilabel>, saj bo to "
"zagotovilo večjo hitrost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:858
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default map font:"
msgstr "Privzeta pisava zemljevida:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default font that gets used on the map."
msgstr "Privzeta pisava, ki se uporablja na zemljevidu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija navigacije"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Navigation configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo navigacije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Navigation configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo navigacije</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inertial globe rotation"
msgstr "Inercialno vrtenje globusa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &marble; will use kinetic spinning while dragging the map. You "
"can turn this behavior off using this check box."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &marble; bo med vlečenjem zemljevida uporabljal kinetično vrtenje. "
"To vedenje lahko izklopite s tem potrditvenim poljem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Animate voyage to the target"
msgstr "Animirajte potovanje do cilja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When searching for a location &marble; can either move instantly to the new "
"location or it can show a travel animation from the previous place to the "
"new place."
msgstr ""
"Pri iskanju lokacije &marble; se lahko takoj premakne na novo lokacijo ali "
"pa prikaže animacijo potovanja s prejšnjega mesta na novo mesto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse view rotation"
msgstr "Vrtenje pogleda miške"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:893
#, no-c-format
msgid "The map and mouse movement is aligned while panning."
msgstr "Zemljevid in gibanje miške sta med premikanjem usklajena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid "On Startup:"
msgstr "Na začetku:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &marble; will display the home location immediately after the "
"application has started. As an alternative it can also show the last "
"position that was active when the user left the application."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &marble; bo prikazal domačo lokacijo takoj po zagonu aplikacije. "
"Kot alternativo lahko prikaže tudi zadnji položaj, ki je bil aktiven, ko je "
"uporabnik zapustil aplikacijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:902
#, no-c-format
msgid "External editor:"
msgstr "Zunanji urejevalnik:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:903
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can define the default editor for the maps or choose "
"<guilabel>Always ask</guilabel> if &marble; should ask you to choose before "
"starting the external editor."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko določite privzeti urejevalnik za zemljevide ali izberete "
"<guilabel>Vedno vprašaj</guilabel>, če &marble; pred zagonom zunanjega "
"urejevalnika zahteva, da izberete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:909
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cache &amp; Proxy Configuration"
msgstr "Predpomnilnik &amp; Konfiguracija posrednika"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Cache &amp; Proxy configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Predpomnilnik &amp; Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo posrednega "
"strežnika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Cache &amp; Proxy configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Predpomnilnik &amp; Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo posrednega "
"strežnika</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cache"
msgstr "Predpomnilnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two caches being used for &marble;: The <guilabel>Physical memory:"
"</guilabel> which is needed to keep map data in the computer's memory. "
"Increasing the value will make the application more responsive. The "
"<guilabel>Hard disc:</guilabel> memory cache is used by download contents "
"from the Internet (&eg; Wikipedia data or map data). Decrease this value if "
"you want to save space on the hard disc and if high usage of the Internet is "
"not an issue."
msgstr ""
"Za &marble; se uporabljata dva predpomnilnika: <guilabel>Fizični pomnilnik:</"
"guilabel>, ki je potreben za shranjevanje zemljevidnih podatkov v pomnilniku "
"računalnika. Če povečate vrednost, bo aplikacija bolj odzivna. "
"<guilabel>Trdi disk:</guilabel> predpomnilnik se uporablja za prenos vsebine "
"iz interneta (&eg; podatkov Wikipedije ali zemljevidov). Zmanjšajte to "
"vrednost, če želite prihraniti prostor na trdem disku in če velika uporaba "
"interneta ne predstavlja težave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Proxy"
msgstr "Posrednik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Proxy settings for your local intranet. Please leave empty if there is no "
"proxy."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve posrednega strežnika za vaš lokalni intranet. Če ni posrednika, "
"pustite prazno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date &amp; Time Configuration"
msgstr "Datum &amp; Konfiguracija časa"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Date &amp; Time configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Datum &amp; Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo časa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Date &amp; Time configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Datum &amp; Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo časa</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:945
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time Zone"
msgstr "Časovni pas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can choose a time zone for &marble;: <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time\">UTC</ulink>, system time "
"zone or choose custom time zone. The chosen option changes the map view only "
"if the map can show the light conditions on the surface."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete časovni pas za &marble;: <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time\">UTC</ulink>, sistemski "
"časovni pas ali izberete časovni pas po meri. Izbrana možnost spremeni "
"pogled zemljevida le, če zemljevid lahko prikaže svetlobne razmere na "
"površini."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid "When &marble; starts"
msgstr "Ko se &marble; zažene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can choose the date and time which will be used on &marble; start: "
"system time or the last session time."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete datum in uro, ki bosta uporabljena na zagonu &marble;: "
"sistemski čas ali čas zadnje seje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronization Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija sinhronizacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; can upload route and bookmark data to <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/OwnCloud\">ownCloud</ulink> server and synchronize them "
"between &marble; instances installed on different devices."
msgstr ""
"&marble; lahko naloži podatke o poti in zaznamke na strežnik <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OwnCloud\">ownCloud</ulink> in jih "
"sinhronizira med &marble; pojavki, nameščeni na različnih napravah."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Synchronization configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo sinhronizacije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Synchronization configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo sinhronizacije</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable synchronization"
msgstr "Omogoči sinhronizacijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The synchronization can be enabled or disabled using this item. When the "
"synchronization is enabled you can choose whether to synchronize route and "
"bookmark data using the corresponding check boxes or press the "
"<guibutton>Sync now</guibutton> button to initiate synchronization "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"S tem elementom lahko omogočite ali onemogočite sinhronizacijo. Ko je "
"sinhronizacija omogočena, lahko izberete, ali želite sinhronizirati podatke "
"o poti in zaznamkih z uporabo ustreznih potrditvenih polj ali pritisnite "
"gumb <guibutton>Sinhroniziraj zdaj</guibutton>, da takoj začnete "
"sinhronizacijo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credentials"
msgstr "Poverilnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can enter your ownClowd credentials. More information on ownClowd "
"configuration can be found on the <ulink url=\"https://owncloud.com/"
"\">ownClowd official website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko vnesete svoje lastne poverilnice za Clowd. Več informacij o "
"konfiguraciji OwnClowd lahko najdete na <ulink url=\"https://owncloud.com/"
"\">uradni spletni strani OwnClowd</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routing Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija usmerjanja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Routing configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo usmerjanja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Routing configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo usmerjanja</phrase>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add..."
msgstr "Dodaj..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:997
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a window where you can add a new routing profile."
msgstr "Odpre okno, kjer lahko dodate nov profil usmerjanja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure..."
msgstr "Konfiguriraj..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a window where the currently selected routing profile can be "
"configured."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno, kjer je mogoče konfigurirati trenutno izbrani profil usmerjanja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Odstrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the selected routing profile."
msgstr "Izbriše izbrani profil usmerjanja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Up"
msgstr "Pomakni se navzgor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selected routing profile is moved up one step. It will appear before the "
"one that was previously on top of it."
msgstr ""
"Izbrani profil usmerjanja se premakne za en korak navzgor. Prikazal se bo "
"pred tistim, ki je bil prej na vrhu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Down"
msgstr "Premik navzdol"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selected routing profile is moved down one step. It will appear after "
"the one that was previously below of it."
msgstr ""
"Izbrani profil usmerjanja se premakne za en korak navzdol. Pojavil se bo za "
"tistim, ki je bil prej pod njim."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija vtičnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Plugin Configuration</guilabel> widget is the place to "
"activate (or deactivate) Info Boxes, Online Services and other plugins that "
"affect the look of &marble;. Active plugins appear in the <guilabel>View</"
"guilabel> menu where you can toggle their visibility."
msgstr ""
"Gradnik <guilabel>Konfiguracija vtičnikov</guilabel> je mesto za aktiviranje "
"(ali deaktiviranje) informacijskih okenc, spletnih storitev in drugih "
"vtičnikov, ki vplivajo na videz &marble;. Aktivni vtičniki se prikažejo v "
"meniju <guilabel>Pogled</guilabel>, kjer lahko spreminjate njihovo vidnost."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1029
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Plugins configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo vtičnikov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Plugins configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo vtičnikov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each plugin can be activated and deactivated using the check box on the "
"left. Some plugins provide further configuration options which are "
"accessible by clicking on the tool icon on the right."
msgstr ""
"Vsak vtičnik je mogoče aktivirati in deaktivirati s potrditvenim poljem na "
"levi. Nekateri vtičniki ponujajo dodatne konfiguracijske možnosti, do "
"katerih lahko dostopate s klikom na ikono orodja na desni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid "Amateur Radio Aprs Plugin"
msgstr "Radioamaterski vtičnik Aprs"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Retrieves data from the Automatic Packet Reporting System via the Internet, "
"a file or a serial device. The position and status of data senders is "
"displayed in the map and updated in real-time."
msgstr ""
"Pridobi podatke iz sistema za samodejno poročanje paketov prek interneta, "
"datoteke ali serijske naprave. Položaj in status pošiljateljev podatkov sta "
"prikazana na zemljevidu in posodobljena v realnem času."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Annotation"
msgstr "Opomba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to add annotations on the maps."
msgstr "Omogoča dodajanje opomb na zemljevide."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid "Atmosphere"
msgstr "Atmosfera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays atmosphere effects."
msgstr "Prikazuje učinke atmosfere."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compass"
msgstr "Kompas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows a compass in the map."
msgstr "Prikazuje kompas na zemljevidu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1061
#, no-c-format
msgid "Coordinate Grid"
msgstr "Koordinatna mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a coordinate grid (you can choose the colors of the grid lines)."
msgstr "Prikaže koordinatno mrežo (lahko izberete barve mrežnih črt)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid "Crosshairs"
msgstr "Nitni križ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable this to display a small crosshair in the center of the map."
msgstr "Omogočite to, da prikaže majhen nitni križ na sredini zemljevida."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Download Progress Indicator"
msgstr "Indikator napredka prenosa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A pie chart on top of the map that shows the progress of ongoing downloads."
msgstr ""
"Krožni grafikon na vrhu zemljevida, ki prikazuje napredek tekočih prenosov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid "Earthquakes"
msgstr "Potresi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the earthquake markers on the map."
msgstr "Na zemljevidu prikaže oznake potresov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eclipses"
msgstr "Mrki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the data about Solar and Moon eclipses."
msgstr "Prikaže podatke o sončnih in luninih mrkih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "Elevation Profile"
msgstr "Višinski profil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the elevation profile overlay for <link linkend=\"routing\">the "
"routes on the map</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže prekrivni profil višinskega profila za <link linkend=\"routing"
"\">poti na zemljevidu</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid "Elevation Profile Marker"
msgstr "Oznaka višinskega profila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid "Marks the current elevation of the elevation profile on the map."
msgstr "Označuje trenutno višino višinskega profila na zemljevidu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid "GpsInfo"
msgstr "GPSInfo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a float item that provides <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> information."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže lebdeči element, ki zagotavlja informacije <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1101
#, no-c-format
msgid "License"
msgstr "Licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays a float item that provides copyright information."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže lebdeči element, ki zagotavlja informacije o avtorskih pravicah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Measure Tool"
msgstr "Orodje za merjenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin to <link linkend=\"measure-distances\">measure distances between "
"two or more points</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik za <link linkend=\"measure-distances\">merjenje razdalj med dvema "
"ali več točkami</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displaying of the distance and the bearing between the points can be "
"configured after pressing the tool icon. It is enough to check the "
"corresponding item to make &marble; show the labels or uncheck the item to "
"hide the labels."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz razdalje in smeri med točkami lahko konfigurirate po pritisku na "
"ikono orodja. Dovolj je označiti ustrezen element, da &marble; pokaže oznake "
"ali odstrani potrditev elementa, da skrije oznake."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Navigacija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the mouse control to zoom and move as float item on the map."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže kontrolnik miške za povečavo in premikanje kot lebdeči element na "
"zemljevidu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid "OSM Mapper Notes"
msgstr "Opombe OSM Mapper"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Implementation of geocoding notes."
msgstr "Implementacija geokodiranja opomb."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1128
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenDesktop Items"
msgstr "Elementi OpenDesktop"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows <ulink url=\"https://opendesktop.org/\">OpenDesktop</ulink> users' "
"avatars and some extra information about them on the map."
msgstr ""
"Na zemljevidu prikaže avatarje uporabnikov <ulink url=\"https://opendesktop."
