#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview Map"
msgstr "Pregled Zemljevida"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1134
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a float item that provides an overview map."
msgstr "To je lebdeči element, ki ponuja pregledni zemljevid."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Photos"
msgstr "Fotografije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically downloads images from around the world in preference to their "
"popularity."
msgstr "Samodejno prenese slike z vsega sveta glede na njihovo priljubljenost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places"
msgstr "Mesta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays trending <ulink url=\"https://foursquare.com/\">Foursquare</ulink> "
"places."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže priljubljena mesta <ulink url=\"https://foursquare.com/"
"\">Foursquare</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position Marker"
msgstr "Oznaka položaja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Draws a marker at the current <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> position."
msgstr ""
"Nariše oznako na trenutnem položaju <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Postal Codes"
msgstr "Poštne številke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postal_code\">postal codes</"
"ulink> of the area on the map."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Postal_code\">poštne "
"številke</ulink> območja na zemljevidu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Routing"
msgstr "Usmerjanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the <link linkend=\"routing\">routing information</link> and "
"navigation controls."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže <link linkend=\"routing\">informacije o poti</link> in navigacijske "
"elemente."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Satellites"
msgstr "Sateliti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the Earth and other planets natural and artificial satellites and "
"their orbits."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže naravne in umetne satelite Zemlje in drugih planetov ter njihove "
"orbite."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scale Bar"
msgstr "Vrstica lestvice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a float item that provides a map scale."
msgstr "To je lebdeči element, ki zagotavlja merilo zemljevida."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speedometer"
msgstr "Merilnik hitrosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the current cruising speed. Needs some <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink> data."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje trenutno potovalno hitrost. Potrebuje nekaj podatkov <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Global_Positioning_System\">GPS</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stars"
msgstr "Zvezde"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1179
#, no-c-format
msgid "A plugin that shows the Starry Sky."
msgstr "Vtičnik, ki prikazuje zvezdnato nebo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1183
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Sun</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Sonce</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "A plugin that shows the Sun."
msgstr "Vtičnik, ki prikazuje sonce."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Weather"
msgstr "Vreme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Downloads current weather information of cities and displays them in the map."
msgstr ""
"Prenese trenutne vremenske informacije mest in jih prikaže na zemljevidu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wikipedia Articles"
msgstr "Članki Wikipedije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically downloads Wikipedia articles and shows them on the right "
"position on the map."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno prenese članke iz Wikipedije in jih prikaže na pravem mestu na "
"zemljevidu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I cannot see my house on the map / Why should I use &marble; if there is "
"<application>Google Earth</application> already?"
msgstr ""
"Ne vidim svoje hiše na zemljevidu / Zakaj naj uporabljam &marble; če že "
"obstaja <application>Google Earth</application>?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; aims to be a lightweight fast educational geographical browser that "
"easily runs on any platform that is supported by &Qt;. While higher "
"resolution maps would be nice to have they aren't necessary for every user "
"and every use case (just like you don't use a full blown text processor each "
"time you just need a simple editor). Also notice &marble; is free software "
"and is based on data that can be freely redistributed in the same way that "
"applies to Free Software."
msgstr ""
"&marble; želi biti lahek in hiter izobraževalni geografski brskalnik, ki "
"zlahka deluje na kateri koli platformi, ki jo podpira &Qt;. Čeprav bi bilo "
"dobro imeti zemljevide z višjo ločljivostjo, niso potrebni za vsakega "
"uporabnika in vsak primer uporabe (tako kot ne uporabljate polnega "
"besedilnega procesorja vsakič, ko potrebujete samo preprost urejevalnik). "
"Upoštevajte tudi da je &marble; prosta programska oprema in temelji na "
"podatkih, ki jih je mogoče prosto distribuirati na enak način, kot velja za "
"prosto programsko opremo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Why is &marble; so fast although I don't have hardware acceleration "
"enabled? / Why doesn't &marble; run smoothly on my expensive 3D graphics "
"card?"
msgstr ""
"Zakaj je &marble; tako hiter, čeprav nimam omogočenega strojnega "
"pospeševanja? / Zakaj &marble; ni gladko deloval na moji dragi 3D grafični "
"kartici?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Despite depicting the earth as a globe &marble; doesn't make use of any 3D "
"hardware acceleration. This has the advantage of running at a decent speed "
"on any platform and hardware supported by &Qt;. However it has the "
"disadvantage that it doesn't run as smoothly as it could if it used hardware "
"accelerated OpenGL. &marble; just uses plain 2D graphics and therefore "
"requires a graphics adapter that is fast at drawing 2D graphics. We plan to "
"add an optional OpenGL backend in the future."
msgstr ""
"Kljub temu, da prikazuje zemljo kot globus &marble; ne uporablja nobenega 3D "
"strojnega pospeševanja. Prednost tega je, da deluje s spodobno hitrostjo na "
"kateri koli platformi in strojni opremi, ki jo podpira &Qt;. Vendar ima to "
"pomanjkljivost, da ne deluje tako gladko, kot bi lahko, če bi uporabljal "
"strojno pospešen OpenGL. &marble; uporablja samo navadno 2D grafiko in zato "
"potrebuje grafični adapter, ki je hiter pri risanju 2D grafike. V "
"prihodnosti nameravamo dodati neobvezno zaledje OpenGL."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Will I ever have to pay for &marble;?"
msgstr "Bom kdaj moral plačati za &marble;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No, never. But the authors always welcome feedback. &marble; is licensed "
"under the <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#LGPL"
"\">LGPL</ulink>, so you will never have to pay for this program."
msgstr ""
"Ne nikoli. Toda avtorji so vedno veseli povratnih informacij. &marble; je "
"licenciran pod <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#LGPL"
"\">LGPL</ulink>, tako da vam za ta program nikoli ne bo treba plačati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1233
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I contribute?"
msgstr "Kako lahko prispevam?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&marble; is not only an application but also a Free Software project. As "
"such it's easy to join: just contact us via the marble-devel mailing list "
"(marble-devel@kde.org)."
msgstr ""
"&marble; ni samo aplikacija, ampak tudi projekt proste programske opreme. "
"Zato se je preprosto pridružiti: samo kontaktirajte nas prek poštnega "
"seznama marble-devel (marble-devel@kde.org)."

